# Realtime Chat Application

## Features
- User Authentication
- Realtime Messaging
- Online Users
- Typing Indicator
- JWT Authentication
- SQLite Database

## Tech Stack
- React.js
- Node.js
- Express.js
- Socket.io
- SQLite
- Sequelize

## Setup

### Frontend
cd client
npm install
npm run dev

### Backend
cd server
npm install
npm run dev